{"tid":342182,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企比樓下氣味滋擾 有冇對策？","createTime":"2017-07-31T11:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T03:25:40.000Z","uid":14090,"like":10,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0269a5b31d2d1c13f57dd88d5aa02dc878eaa9cc","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:43:13.000Z","msg":"小弟住村屋<br />\n<br />\n樓下日日點蚊香 放係條公用樓梯到 啲煙日日攻到上黎我地屋企<br />\n其實佢樓下樓梯個窗係唔開 仲加多把鎖唔比我地散走啲煙<br />\n<br />\n我地試左好多方法搞呢單野<br />\n1）試過拍門同佢地好聲好氣傾過 點知冇左回事<br />\n2）試過同管理公司講過 又冇左回事<br />\n3）試過叫警察上門 點知個次比樓下兩個廢老屌返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁算 我地係我地個層開下窗 放啲毛巾係門「拿」等啲煙攻唔到入黎 點知呢幾日 兩條廢老愈黎愈過份 將個蚊香愈放愈上 啲煙愈黎愈勁<br />\n樓下個窗本身話可以開既 依家加左把鎖開唔到<br />\n<br />\n屋企人搞呢單野都搞左好耐 有冇咩方法可以搞掂呢個問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4885e148e0a37b69cf8da206739e4fcce36903","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:43:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c92834d418abae945b10631303d45c455cb71410","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:45:57.000Z","msg":"Push push push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a771c6a27429bd03d72cd59a002f9010367269b","tid":342182,"uid":24785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:46:38.000Z","msg":"拎條水喉水落去"},{"pid":"8cbbc45f5d93a512cff45602207b67bdbc3a9648","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:46:44.000Z","msg":"有冇法律jj幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我媽氣管唔好 想快快手搞掂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed50f6e524ced1090baa20ff46fad66a03642d3f","tid":342182,"uid":24785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎條水喉射水落去</blockquote>"},{"pid":"61f69c6abb9c787b10a66a48accd4e9f2ec57445","tid":342182,"uid":33572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"深夜果陣睇av<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開埋個喇叭"},{"pid":"536a4be45e94d224fcb0cb7bc8a1349d067c3ae8","tid":342182,"uid":3066,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:48:06.000Z","msg":"見一次就淋一次水"},{"pid":"14c7c9e2f31a4c7ba7877969c080957f027e02a9","tid":342182,"uid":18702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:48:14.000Z","msg":"射水啦 排蚊香濕水都點唔著<br />\n睇佢乾得快定你射得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f7ccb1e0f346b5b7c57d9a5616991655f46330","tid":342182,"uid":101513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:50:41.000Z","msg":"裝個電子驅蚊，大家開心"},{"pid":"9f4be975cf820a25217962593e67aea2b9e8f0c3","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"個次報警 兩條廢老發哂爛渣 話香港邊條法例唔比點蚊香 仲屌柒我地話我地仆街陷家剷<br />\n<br />\n我地一直好聲好氣同佢地傾 仲比左啲其他防蚊方法比佢地 佢地都唔accept  都算 依家佢地做啲野根本損人不利己<br />\n<br />\n依家佢個窗裝左鎖 根本唔會開窗 所以唔會有蚊 但佢依家個蚊香日點夜點 仲要愈放愈上 愈黎愈離譜 我地忍無可忍 根本就係想激嬲我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求各位巴絲打獻上良策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590382b89d97e2c3caf7f3a41f5c98833b8fb0b9","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>裝個電子驅蚊，大家開心</blockquote><br />\n建議過佢地 廢老好撚硬頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8602a3f505a83b83a95b5d7af29511e335eb2b28","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>射水啦 排蚊香濕水都點唔著<br />\n睇佢乾得快定你射得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一陣比人告返轉頭咪仲衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96748b82268ece30b6a07a0ce691d87ac19de1c","tid":342182,"uid":101513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>裝個電子驅蚊，大家開心</blockquote><br />\n建議過佢地 廢老好撚硬頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你蝕底d出錢裝，有限錢，身體要緊"},{"pid":"5d2ff329b0576528264d438835ed3464b720e8dc","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:54:06.000Z","msg":"電子蚊香 驅蚊機 驅蚊草 蚊網 全部都試過同佢講過 <br />\n<br />\n仲要係超級好聲好氣 比過建議佢 仲打算大家夾錢裝蚊網 始終我地都會經過個到 諗住夾下錢 但佢地都唔肯<br />\n<br />\n依家愈黎愈離譜 發覺呢個社會好人永遠比人恰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ee6d503c7979c8efd9d3bc4a83344152ff4306","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>裝個電子驅蚊，大家開心</blockquote><br />\n建議過佢地 廢老好撚硬頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你蝕底d出錢裝，有限錢，身體要緊</blockquote><br />\n有講過話出錢裝 佢地都唔肯 仲反問我地話香港邊條法例唔比點蚊香"},{"pid":"da9709b9fd7a40e73b4b5ce5484a6ba17eb7197f","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>深夜果陣睇av<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開埋個喇叭</blockquote><br />\n一陣咪比老母撞破我睇av<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dea61f657ff19e80a4f5bdbc385055cdf9123ca","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:56:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見一次就淋一次水</blockquote><br />\n一陣比佢告返轉頭仲衰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98fd17b3d9e50a52b1e1240924d9fc17bc2059b","tid":342182,"uid":6332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:57:45.000Z","msg":"係佢屋企門口燒炭<br />\n日日洗樓梯 沖沖水就算<br />\n記得放個小心地滑 同每日清洗時間<br />\n話說有窗姐 大風d加粒石仔就得啦"},{"pid":"23f8ecba124a459cf26e71d8b3e5c3221067412d","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係佢屋企門口燒炭<br />\n日日洗樓梯 沖沖水就算<br />\n記得放個小心地滑 同每日清洗時間<br />\n話說有窗姐 大風d加粒石仔就得啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n燒炭就不了<br />\n<br />\n下面個個可以諗諗<br />\n<br />\n但唔明石仔個到"},{"pid":"ef7bcdb697f23d63d9bfc6971fda6dc9b3919e52","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:00:12.000Z","msg":"一直好好對佢地 唔知點解要針對我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278f338f659c75c57f3fbb17e7d309f7e87bdeca","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714ea32b36241c6a014e999cdb78245746d59588","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:01:53.000Z","msg":"係咪個廢老負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0775638fde60e4045f50fe3190e05797adf58bcc","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:02:55.000Z","msg":"仲試過去同政府部門投訴 點知比人耍走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實係咪有得跟進？"},{"pid":"5f12ca40dd383ba83bbeb6b62fbef954b0cf4142","tid":342182,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直好好對佢地 唔知點解要針對我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢老無個樣整個樣"},{"pid":"1e5420120cbad6bc6453b7ae10109e3094a0f6b9","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一直好好對佢地 唔知點解要針對我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢老無個樣整個樣</blockquote><br />\n死老野 好撚固執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b682a48a04ca6021dbaadcee1ee383ba498c1f0","tid":342182,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:10:34.000Z","msg":"d老野如果仲有重男輕女既固執<br />\n佢地永遠都唔會改變<br />\n所以你點同佢地講<br />\n都係曬9氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9a4cfc7b19703c3a9136502d32d41ca6055e3e","tid":342182,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係佢屋企門口燒炭<br />\n日日洗樓梯 沖沖水就算<br />\n記得放個小心地滑 同每日清洗時間<br />\n話說有窗姐 大風d加粒石仔就得啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n燒炭就不了<br />\n<br />\n下面個個可以諗諗<br />\n<br />\n但唔明石仔個到</blockquote><br />\n隻窗有時無啦啦會碎&hellip;大自然嘅力量好大架&hellip;"},{"pid":"27339ab88d7ec899a86ecd8f1a6f9a5105e70fa7","tid":342182,"uid":32699,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:13:45.000Z","msg":"事實你係可以告佢滋擾既<br />\n只要你證明到佢做緊既行為/佢既設施令你受到影響就得<br />\n<br />\n你可以買個空氣指數計先<br />\n計返佢地有點蚊香同無點果陣既分別<br />\n你有讀數做一個客觀性既指標應該有得打<br />\n<br />\n而你下次開始建議樓下做其他野去防蚊果陣<br />\n你應該係用書面通知<br />\n比管理處留份底再由管理處轉交樓下<br />\n重點係比管理處留底知你幾月幾日有咩訴求同曾經比咩建議樓下<br />\n比管理處有個記錄留底先 <br />\n到時要上庭點都有用<br />\n<br />\n如果管理處有同你開case既<br />\n你都可以問佢地拎份書面報告去同律師傾點做<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601df46c5b67fd6e89e5a251938f6ab306d078a5","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:08:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係佢屋企門口燒炭<br />\n日日洗樓梯 沖沖水就算<br />\n記得放個小心地滑 同每日清洗時間<br />\n話說有窗姐 大風d加粒石仔就得啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n燒炭就不了<br />\n<br />\n下面個個可以諗諗<br />\n<br />\n但唔明石仔個到</blockquote><br />\n隻窗有時無啦啦會碎&hellip;大自然嘅力量好大架&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廢時搞到成地玻璃碎 咪又係盞搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63ba2e5e8e26ef3b24695ce8483c8330b971197","tid":342182,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:09:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事實你係可以告佢滋擾既<br />\n只要你證明到佢做緊既行為/佢既設施令你受到影響就得<br />\n<br />\n你可以買個空氣指數計先<br />\n計返佢地有點蚊香同無點果陣既分別<br />\n你有讀數做一個客觀性既指標應該有得打<br />\n<br />\n而你下次開始建議樓下做其他野去防蚊果陣<br />\n你應該係用書面通知<br />\n比管理處留份底再由管理處轉交樓下<br />\n重點係比管理處留底知你幾月幾日有咩訴求同曾經比咩建議樓下<br />\n比管理處有個記錄留底先 <br />\n到時要上庭點都有用<br />\n<br />\n如果管理處有同你開case既<br />\n你都可以問佢地拎份書面報告去同律師傾點做<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打好詳盡 試試佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打做律師定係又係比人滋擾過？"},{"pid":"2dfba3041500dbe606847a53273ce60bd86112c3","tid":342182,"uid":59580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:30:11.000Z","msg":"蚊香有火喎"},{"pid":"52a25df2dbede7b9ff6b5d6806eb14fbc4dfa794","tid":342182,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:37:03.000Z","msg":"軟既唔得就黎堅架啦<br />\n仲同佢慢慢顛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f31b260bad1cde027f1253a67ab54cf8511590","tid":342182,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"波子。。。棋。。。"},{"pid":"4fd85b047e86e17301bc8cc6f26c358b3ef7c2b7","tid":342182,"uid":63734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:11:52.000Z","msg":"淘寶個震牆器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5207609a41c2a83b91c9ebe7fa852f4741b4a0da","tid":342182,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>事實你係可以告佢滋擾既<br />\n只要你證明到佢做緊既行為/佢既設施令你受到影響就得<br />\n<br />\n你可以買個空氣指數計先<br />\n計返佢地有點蚊香同無點果陣既分別<br />\n你有讀數做一個客觀性既指標應該有得打<br />\n<br />\n而你下次開始建議樓下做其他野去防蚊果陣<br />\n你應該係用書面通知<br />\n比管理處留份底再由管理處轉交樓下<br />\n重點係比管理處留底知你幾月幾日有咩訴求同曾經比咩建議樓下<br />\n比管理處有個記錄留底先 <br />\n到時要上庭點都有用<br />\n<br />\n如果管理處有同你開case既<br />\n你都可以問佢地拎份書面報告去同律師傾點做<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n