quote><br />\n鬼知係你淋咩<br />\n人地都唔怕你告，你驚乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa14e2af8939487f97b8edb4547db0818c9ab58","tid":342182,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"小心d呀 萬一反擊個廢老發癲日日拍門鬧你地屋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廢事越搞越衰呀 多一事不如少一事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乜鳩都怕不如縮番入老母個閪到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c66c23a8a5f623773b069bddfbffd46cae3ce0","tid":342182,"uid":92201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T06:22:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵消防？唔開窗有機會火警散唔到煙有危險</blockquote><br />\ncontrol fire 無犯法啊, <br />\n報火警就得"},{"pid":"030699f78f917f9424512f5d7b8545a6460de2be","tid":342182,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T06:33:23.000Z","msg":"係正你樓下就易攪啦，買個共振喇叭貼住地板，每晚都同佢地分享同音樂，我個人比較喜歡住生咒同死佈片既配樂，亦都會錄低自己對鄰里和睦既見解，日日提醒自己鄰里關係既重要。<br />\n<br />\n我敢擔保唔駛一星期佢地主動收皮！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=4891631\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D4891631&d=3MZ9oywrux%2BqS8jML%2FF7ZU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=97b07fd2\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=4891631</a><br />\n<br />\n利申：住村屋炸過樓下"},{"pid":"bdc1b39735e1ad2116f6da7f07fc0f2e8164a111","tid":342182,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T06:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淘寶個震牆器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n震埋自己就咪搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢想講共振喇叭，其實你自己搵野隔一隔就唔會點聽到聲，但樓下就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"b62eaaf521b37408392d23cc892484b27437